citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:00 pm on
09-Mar-20.
The inspector arrived at the facility at approximately 1:00 pm and spoke to an individual at the facility who stated
that no one was available for the inspection. The inspector then left the facility.
